---
title: Sesame-Crumbed Pork & Garlic Broccoli with Ginger Rice & Japanese Mayo
description: Steamed rice gets a special touch when it’s infused with ginger. It’s the perfect base for crumbed pork and Japanese mayo so you can taste a home-cooked Japanese feast with ease!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sesame-crumbed-pork-garlic-veggies-cf8f9ff9.jpg
